These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
House: tower, futuristic
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the colombian##3
2. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the tower house##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| House      | tower  | futuristic   |
| Hobby   | skydiving     | magic-tricks   |
| Nationality         | colombian | nigerian |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, snooker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, metal
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, chef
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the chef is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of funk is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Game          | monopoly     | snooker |
| Music-Genre   | metal | funk  |
| Job           | chef         | coach     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, march
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, cricket
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, classical
1. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Birthday    | march     | december |
| Sport         | cricket | basketball    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Music-Genre   | metal         | classical    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bolivar
House: ranch-style, cottage
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, azalea
1. the cottage house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Cigar          | bolivar   | montecristo  |
| House         | ranch-style | cottage     |
| Flower   | tulip  | azalea         |

 #################################

 
