2 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle
City: edinburgh, new-york
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the palace house##3
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Beverage           | coffee | iced-tea |
| House   | palace    | farmhouse      |
| Pet           | mouse      | turtle          |
| City         | new-york | edinburgh       |

